{
  "logNo": "223767966049",
  "title": "셀프 포토북 제작 아기 성장 여행 웨딩앨범까지 점보포토가 좋은 이유",
  "date": "2025-02-21",
  "labels": [
    "상품 소개"
  ],
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a3d04ca-0817-4995-be3c-dfdb0713913d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223767966049/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eaf66027-4f94-43e8-8f52-7641d1dafcbc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2dc4df11-2098-43cf-86f2-b2bbe8f019b4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c982594a-57ff-44a0-8788-7a762d1ef8cb\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-769ddeb6-6f52-42da-9bf5-9bc42a82eda4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b028de5c-02b8-415f-aa6a-19159166ce47\" style=\"\">요즘 스마트폰 카메라 기술이 발전하면서 특별한 순간을 직접 찍는 분들이 많으십니다. 태아 초음파부터 아기가 성장하는 순간들, 처음으로 하는 해외여행, 부모님 생일, 그리고 웨딩까지, 굳이 스튜디오에 가지 않아도 된 거지요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-952b043b-7399-4712-b795-a22bc0b51df4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-df1b0115-961a-4bce-a6ed-93fefa9df8d3\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a28c704d-47cb-4546-aae8-c73c4197fbc8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-9be3710b-bd55-40fb-b099-857e6b77cb46\" style=\"\">하지만 시간이 지나면서 핸드폰 앨범 속에 보관되고 잊히곤 하는데요. 그래서 요즘 셀프 포토북 제작이 인기랍니다. 직접 고른 사진을 예쁘게 편집하고 세상 하나뿐만 나만의 책으로 만들면, 오랫동안 간직할 수 있으니까요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-41d7fcc6-607c-4ce4-adb7-5cfaa75c0a87\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-cad4a3c9-ddd1-4079-8bf9-b78141043346\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3e85dfb1-d299-4d01-a1a7-8b823027981d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-540df775-d69d-4e4b-8bc8-42adb3e0225a\" style=\"\"><b>다양한 사이트가 있지만, 그중에서도 점보포토를 많이 이용하시는데요. 부담스럽지 않은 가격에 강남 스튜디오 수준의 품질로 사랑받고 있답니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9480d152-2295-4948-98da-e347ba5ab97e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-990dd486-281a-43b9-ac0b-5ff02f083364\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-750f648c-890e-4139-ba5f-e71a738d6d1f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3bacce5e-b19b-47a3-8546-c423dceb128a\" style=\"\">그럼 이제 왜 점포포토에서 하면 좋을지 자세히 알려드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4718f6b2-79db-4564-bdf5-1403df09e25d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-6bf5262b-5d9b-45a0-baec-280568617747\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-97656330-4d7a-4fdf-8039-be9fd23f19ff\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1432fc6f-e75d-438d-9369-6e3aedeff774\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-18da0a81-ce08-4b5f-8acd-e53732728226\" style=\"\">목차</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1aec03f8-c764-4910-905a-544ac66a3d11\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-4dda413d-d65c-40ab-aa53-0767d40cd8f9\" style=\"\">1) 포토북이란?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-06e0dc2d-3070-4707-8fb4-c5e4b8f55181\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2df0b52d-3785-40e0-8bdc-f25d4700b1b3\" style=\"\">2) 셀프 포토북 제작 방법, 점보포토에서는 어렵지 않답니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-347fc825-e8ca-405e-8f26-4d485ece6d2a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-430f5cde-bbfe-4677-84db-d5ebc4fe982e\" style=\"\">3) 점보포토 셀프 포토북 제작, 이런 점이 다릅니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1e54c87a-e6dc-435e-8433-3baa6676d7a9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-47d1e0ce-407e-41c2-8640-7fc710bc30ab\" style=\"\">4) 셀프 포토북 제작 이런 분들께 추천드려요! </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-498d13a1-af45-4191-a619-84cc857b4940\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-93a55652-15b0-4d86-b03d-dc36c20cfd26\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-292823f9-8b1d-4f06-80bf-a3c2eb0cc01a\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-41308f20-9ecc-4118-a910-1c5bee356966\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-19932104-ed87-461b-81d8-bdb1cc02092b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1b949192-d9a7-4b0c-b1d0-e61eb90e24e6\" style=\"\"><b>1) 포토북이란?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d8443886-b017-41fb-89d1-92dc830a658f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223767966049/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-83489aed-0157-4d4e-bc54-1740adb0fd5d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-14cfab53-af43-4d78-891c-f23d7158b468\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-13aeafb9-6211-4c16-bf59-6c6322a39c8f\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f24ff37a-aed9-46d6-ac49-482a9d627f02\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-98d41ee8-b126-4e84-9960-0ba30ba93e8e\" style=\"background-color:#b0f1ff;\">내가 가지고 있는 사진을 책으로 만드는 것을 말한답니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-644218e3-66b6-47ee-8962-a53450a1cb05\" style=\"\">한 장씩 인화해서 보관하는 것보다 한 권으로 정리하면 보기도 편하고 추억을 더 특별하게 남길 수 있지요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8c9c8358-c794-483b-af18-9fcbde615dc4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4b63f9c1-6e31-4d13-bc55-7389c376d518\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8bfbb872-2be2-453f-815e-19b874403068\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4bd030b9-d65e-4614-959f-7797a64110bd\" style=\"\">요즘에는 매년 아기 사진첩을 만들어 아이의 성장을 기록하는 부모님들도 많고, 여행의 기억을 정리하는 분들도 늘고 있습니다. 웨딩앨범을 만들어 소중한 순간을 오랫동안 간직하는 신혼부부들도 많지요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9bb6fb09-c5f0-4697-88e1-3386be842a80\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3a8b037f-3c57-4a86-95ef-c2012f64d20b\" style=\"\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-bf6e2094-7c43-4c54-af03-1b05075c9f13\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5f771416-b11e-4df7-9e37-751245bcad87\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b34c0832-3955-4a24-90a2-a7c572ad8cec\" style=\"\"><b>2) 셀프 포토북 제작 방법, 점보포토에서는 어렵지 않답니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f29c5a72-68d7-4b0a-af73-0c42c036abf6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2235f689-6f7f-4f76-ab85-bcd8a7928f5e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-44ce7e25-4cd0-4019-9673-1609623d26a5\" style=\"\">셀프 포토북 제작이 어렵다고 생각할 수도 있지만, </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-04ed2c9f-4c34-4778-bb42-6b32875b109c\" style=\"\"><b>점보포토는 전용 프로그램을 제공하고 있어 누구나 쉽게 간편하고 쉽게 만들 수 있답니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28fc0253-fe6f-4bd4-af00-b6d5fb9d0799\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-1058afb3-e13c-4467-91b1-2daf489ed8cb\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a43a8af-bece-4aad-934b-e2e6be9b9d88\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-179de1fe-9b97-45f0-a584-d24805cc8918\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-49f17961-218a-4073-bed0-514fb9857a76\" style=\"\"><b>그전에, 상품 옵션은 무엇이 있는지 알려드리겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ed3488e9-fb48-4172-a555-68d4937776f8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_l