c1d-a4b4-8f35ddf3ce9d\" style=\"\"><b>페이지 수: 24페이지부터 80페이지까지</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7df9922f-279d-4f70-8620-7e2b6a050bb8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-06279ab4-59f1-4369-bb2a-4e5a56cfacaa\" style=\"\"><b>가격: 합리적인 가격대</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-98404c70-815f-4329-96de-746b66b5543f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-74e344dd-5c6a-4958-bee7-94e8760208ea\" style=\"\"><b>추가 가격 : 2페이지당 1,000원</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0ed0d9ff-c873-4bc5-970a-feda7c90f7dc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-bdd9a766-e077-4abf-9141-cb6a7987758d\" style=\"\"><b>케이스 : 종이 케이스 구매 가능</b></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f47f6623-0d05-4474-add1-2061b02f8b3b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b8d838ff-8e20-43ed-b7e1-5e2b3a6ba020\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bf86ed46-7f0a-418e-957d-97365a705371\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dad78721-98ae-4809-8ba8-c72fc1571dc0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-0121c69d-ea91-4bf1-a349-f1ae31870dac\" style=\"\"><b>포토북은 다양한 종류가 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-45b44ea4-c8ac-4e15-87e1-77c